sequenceDiagram
autonumber
participant User
participant Frontend
participant API
participant Pool
participant DB

User->>Frontend: Vacate booking
Frontend->>API: PATCH /api/bookings/:bookingId/vacate
API->>API: requireAuth
alt Not authenticated
API-->>Frontend: 401 Authentication is required
Frontend-->>User: Show auth error
else Authenticated
API->>API: Validate bookingId and actor employee id
alt Invalid booking id
API-->>Frontend: 400 Invalid booking id
Frontend-->>User: Show validation error
else Valid booking id
alt Invalid authenticated user
API-->>Frontend: 401 Invalid authenticated user
Frontend-->>User: Show auth error
else Valid user
API->>Pool: getConnection + beginTransaction
API->>DB: Select booking FOR UPDATE
alt Booking not found
API->>Pool: rollback
API-->>Frontend: 404 Booking not found
Frontend-->>User: Show not found
else Booking found
API->>API: Check permission (organizer or admin)
alt Not allowed
API->>Pool: rollback
API-->>Frontend: 403 You do not have permission to vacate this booking
Frontend-->>User: Show forbidden
else Allowed
API->>API: Check status
alt Cancelled
API->>Pool: rollback
API-->>Frontend: 400 Cancelled bookings cannot be vacated
Frontend-->>User: Show validation error
else Already vacated
API->>Pool: rollback
API-->>Frontend: 200 Booking is already vacated
Frontend-->>User: Show status
else Status ok
API->>API: Validate timing data
alt Invalid timing data
API->>Pool: rollback
API-->>Frontend: 400 Booking has invalid timing data
Frontend-->>User: Show validation error
else Timing valid
alt Booking not started yet
API->>Pool: rollback
API-->>Frontend: 400 Only ongoing bookings can be vacated
Frontend-->>User: Show validation error
else Booking already completed
API->>Pool: rollback
API-->>Frontend: 200 Booking is already completed
Frontend-->>User: Show status
else Ongoing booking
API->>DB: Update end_time and status to vacated
API->>DB: Insert booking audit
API->>Pool: commit
API-->>Frontend: 200 Booking vacated successfully
Frontend-->>User: Show success
end
end
end
end
end
end
end
